milestones.description: Bevan Congdon has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (6) for NZ, going past Mark Burgess
John Parker has broken the record for most catches in an innings (2) in ODIs for NZ, going past Peter Coman's 1
Glenn Turner has broken the record for most catches (3) in ODIs for NZ, going past Peter Coman's 2
Dayle Hadlee has become the top wicket-taker for NZ in ODIs with 8 wickets, going past Bevan Congdon's 6
England's 136 is the lowest score in ODIs. They broke the earlier record of 158
